# MDSOC Outer-Axis Documentation Header
#
# There is NO shared MDSOC base mixin in `src/lib/` today (confirmed with
# `grep -rln "mdsoc" src/lib/ --include="*.spl"`). This file is documentation
# only — it pins the five outer axes the spostgre and NVFS capsules must
# declare when their MDSOC outer surfaces get written in later phases.
#
# Axes (per doc/04_architecture/mdsoc_architecture_tobe.md "MDSOC+" section):
#
#   1. Modules          — the `.spl` files composing this capsule.
#   2. Dependencies     — upward module imports this capsule consumes.
#   3. Side effects     — classes of external mutation (disk / net / syscalls).
#   4. Capabilities     — capability probes this capsule requires (see
#                         storage.capability.Capability).
#   5. Ownership        — who is allowed to hold / mutate each handle
#                         (ArenaHandle, SealToken, Generation).
#
# When a real MDSOC base mixin lands, this file SHOULD become the canonical
# re-export for that mixin under `std.storage.mdsoc_base`. Until then,
# keep this file header-only — no executable code is emitted.
